&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    Collection and reporting tools&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Task&amp;nbsp;Effort data is collected in IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Team Concert&amp;reg; and IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Project Conductor&amp;reg;. IBM&amp;reg;&#xD;
    Rational&amp;reg; Insight&amp;reg; provides an out of the box report for this metric.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
